What does * { box-sizing: border-box; } do? What are its advantages?
box-sizing:border-box changes algorithm of  counting box-size. it includes margins,
borders, paddings and size of content in contrast to default sizing by content size

Can you explain the difference between coding a web site to be responsive versus using a mobile-first strategy?
Mobile-first strategy is strategy in which heart of design strategy is mobile version of site. Responsive design-site is
automatically adjusted based on size of user screens


